</style><h2 id="outline__4" class="wp-block-heading">古关宝石</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignleft size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc9XeDmp0eYrNZ3GLw_bhmPBPcyj_juxv9JY9kgi34eSmgv0V3yBqvurNpuM6pyEGXW0Vo6bm31IxgsuiVeUiTuk0iSBKFoAGhcxeSmyy4SLLiahDiOXzMJ33pE7PjHX-kkk8V3zbeY8qhrT0W0tF9F9=w781-h1350-s-no" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure></div><p>凝聚人所有情感的“情感水晶”。</p><p>美好的情感和肮脏的情感在岁月中一次次层层叠加，升华为绝世光彩。</p><p>由于历史上许多傻瓜都在争夺远古魔石的光辉，所以它被保密，以免落入任何人的手中。</p><p>当她与人交往，接触到善良的感觉时，她似乎更加闪耀。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>北田莫 (@428clv)</td></tr><tr><td>官方渠道</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@KosekiBijou" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Koseki Bijou Ch. Hololive-EN">Koseki Bijou Ch. Hololive-EN</a></td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）公众号</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/kosekibijou" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="古关宝石🗿holoEN">古关宝石<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5ff.png" alt="🗿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />全息EN</a></td></tr><tr><td>预定首发交付日期</td><td>2023年（令和5年）<br> 7月30日（周日）12:45~ </td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="嘟嘟！" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UCvopJiRdFo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/kosekibijou/status/1684036223554420736" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_9An8-s_DDBKppS6lX0lquGtQQPDgVCfjZwOw9_ZVDechIm61bORpXBqUOg